&lt;h2 id="run-obi"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Run OBI&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#run-obi" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Verify in Splunk APM</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/3-verify-in-splunk/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/2-python-warmup/3-verify-in-splunk/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="check-splunk-apm"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Check Splunk APM&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#check-splunk-apm" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate to &lt;strong&gt;APM&lt;/strong&gt; in Splunk Observability Cloud.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Filter by service name &lt;code&gt;warmup-app&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You should see traces for the &lt;code&gt;/hello&lt;/code&gt; endpoint.
&lt;strong&gt;NOTE: This may take a number of minutes to ingest the first traces&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-just-happened"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;What Just Happened?&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#what-just-happened" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Flask app is &amp;ldquo;naked&amp;rdquo; it has zero observability code. It only knows how to say hello and send a heartbeat metric.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OBI attached eBPF probes to the kernel&amp;rsquo;s networking stack and observed HTTP traffic flowing through your app&amp;rsquo;s process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OBI generated OpenTelemetry-compatible trace spans and sent them directly to Splunk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You just added distributed tracing to a running process from the kernel. No SDK, no code changes, no restart.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>